        {
            "title": "「一換一」趕搭尾班車 稅貸買車更勝貸款上會？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"近期唔少用家憂慮「一換一」計劃將告終，加快步伐換電動車。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nPh5.W0l3sqKeAqm51J1vQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/51d84250-ff4c-11f0-af2b-37a44300e234\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">近期唔少用家憂慮「一換一」計劃將告終，加快步伐換電動車。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">財爺發表新一份預算案時公報，「一換一」計劃在三月底屆滿後不再繼續，即時刺激電動車買家趕搭尾班車。究竟「一換一」慳到幾多？買新車除了貸款上會，用稅貸借力係另一個靈活選擇。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://yfinance.onelink.me/3068494570?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_[…]ub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub3=&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_\" rel=\"sponsored\" target=\"_blank\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">點樣「一換一」 無車都可以買Quota？</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為鼓勵用家購買電動車，政府於2018年推出「一換一」計劃，拆毀及取消合資格私家車登記。並首次登記新電動私家車，可獲首次登記稅寬減，上限為172,500元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c9af8c8a-e7d3-452e-9996-656ab1f26b53-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">想參與「一換一」慳稅，舊私家車要符合三項條件：</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>1.首次登記最少6年（即續牌時要驗車）；</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>2.舊私家車取消登記前，車主為續連18個月或以上登記車主</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>3.劏車前10個月已支付牌費</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">申請「一換一」程序，一般車廠會提供安排劏舊車服務，之後收到「車輛拆毀證明書」，列有舊車資料及劏車公司蓋章。搆同「車輛拆毀證明書」到運輸署，填妥<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:TD184表格;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/filemanager/common/td184_e-fillable_chi.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">TD184表格</a>為舊車取消車輛登記，再提交「替代電動私家車」首次登記申請及「一換一」計劃申請。</p><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, undefined%)\"></div></blockquote><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">搞一輪，借力「一換一」可以平幾多？可以參考Smart#1 Premium例子：</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"資料來源：Smart HK\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"441\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cYYv2N3IxNxEmvOmYwflVw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ0MQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/a9e3a070-ff4c-11f0-9835-49c1cd5d5e72\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:資料來源：Smart HK;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.smart.com/zh_HK/one-for-one/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">資料來源：Smart HK</a></figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">睇以上例子，買車稅款由185,747元勁減至13,247元確係吸引，而且「一換一」計劃不設轉售限制，揸大半年後又想換車，就可以將電動車甩手套現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">無舊車揸手，仍有一個方法參加「一換一」，就係買入舊車Quota。 車行及經紀有配對服務，幫買家買入其他舊車Quota，一般市價約1.3萬元至1.8萬元。不過要符合「一換一」條件，要先由舊車主安排劏車及取消車輛登記，再購買新電動車先登記至舊車主名下，最後才轉到買家名下。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">買Quota最大風險是舊車主要有信用，以往有不良賣家會同時向多名買家出售Quota，收取訂金後失聯，又或舊車車主已經破產，新車主無辜遭追債，如透過經紀或車行配對舊車車主，可要求簽約作實多一重保障。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">趕「死線」出車 借稅貸買車有乜優勢？</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">財爺一錘定音為「一換一」劃下死線，買家在3 月 31 日限期前出牌，尚有一定機會享首次登記稅寬減優惠。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">買車最熱門的融資選擇，是透過車行申請貸款上會。買車上會分租購買（Hire Purchase）及租賃（Leasing）兩種，前者毋須付首期，但利息會較高，後者要支付首期但息率較優惠。車行將你的貸款申請轉介予合作的財務公司後，財務公司會評估車輛價值，一般可借車價90％貸款，再加申請人還款能力及信貸評分計算利率。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"想靈活一點，借稅貸是另一選擇。借20至30萬元稅貸，既可以一筆過買車，亦毋須抵押新車。 (Photo by PETER PARKS/AFP via Getty Images)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_Y9IIOgPFgT.qEZVbCc1pw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/50e05850-ff4d-11f0-adfe-2ac080d5a413\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">想靈活一點，<a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:借稅貸是另一選擇;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%A8%85%E8%B2%B8-%E4%BD%8E%E6%81%AF-%E6%9C%80%E5%B9%B3-%E5%88%A9%E6%81%AF-%E7%A8%85%E5%8B%99%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE-%E5%80%9F%E5%B9%B3%E9%8C%A2-%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87-apr-%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91-%E5%9B%9E%E8%B4%88-%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0-%E9%82%84%E6%AC%BE%E6%9C%9F-084016130.html\">借稅貸是另一選擇</a>。借20至30萬元稅貸，既可以一筆過買車，亦毋須抵押新車。 (Photo by PETER PARKS/AFP via Getty Images)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">買車上會好處係一條龍服務，但由於已將新車抵押，買家須購買全保，並要將牌簿抵押至財務公司。汽車貸款或收取手續費，加上車行會推銷指定汽車美容套餐或延長保固，或會進一步增加出車成本。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">想靈活一點，<a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:借稅貸是另一選擇;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%A8%85%E8%B2%B8-%E4%BD%8E%E6%81%AF-%E6%9C%80%E5%B9%B3-%E5%88%A9%E6%81%AF-%E7%A8%85%E5%8B%99%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE-%E5%80%9F%E5%B9%B3%E9%8C%A2-%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87-apr-%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91-%E5%9B%9E%E8%B4%88-%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0-%E9%82%84%E6%AC%BE%E6%9C%9F-084016130.html\">借稅貸是另一選擇</a>。借20至30萬元稅貸，既可以一筆過買車，亦毋須抵押新車，選購車保及其他額外服務，都可以自己話事。用稅貸借力買車，加上原有買車儲蓄，可以令養車預算更鬆動，例如有更多「筆直」選擇更就腳的月租充電車位，以及加錢選購較特別的顏色及配件。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%8F%9B%E4%B8%80%E3%80%8D%E8%B6%95%E6%90%AD%E5%B0%BE%E7%8F%AD%E8%BB%8A-%E7%A8%85%E8%B2%B8%E8%B2%B7%E8%BB%8A%E6%9B%B4%E5%8B%9D%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%83%EF%BC%9F-041749826.html",
